Class TriangleSetImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • hu.kazocsaba.v3d.mesh.TriangleSetImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IndexedTriangleMesh, PointList, TriangleMesh

    public class TriangleSetImpl
extends Object
implements IndexedTriangleMesh
    A triangle mesh which just stores a list of points. Triangle i is formed by points 3*i, 3*i+1, and 3*i+2.
